data.description: Premier 1-Acre Land in Independence Heights**: This exclusive 1-acre land, precisely dimensioned at 208 ft x 208 ft, is ideally located to support the development of 18 to 22 homes. An exceptional chance for builders and investors, this property offers a unique setup for innovative residential projects in a prestigious area. Its distinct size is a key benefit, facilitating an efficient design that requires only two driveways, optimizing land usage. Situated outside flood risk zones, it guarantees increased stability for any new construction. Pre-existing utilities on site make for a swift development process, adding to its attractiveness. Its closeness to the renowned Kennedy Elementary School enhances its value. Acquire this land to craft a noteworthy presence in the rapidly growing Independence Heights. An essential acquisition for visionary real estate investors. Refer to the attached documents for more information. Plot not yet subdivided.
